    <div class="container">
        <h2>Follow Call Dan on social media</h2>
        <p>
            Keep in touch with Call Dan on Facebook and stay updated with our
            latest handyman tips, news, and service specials.
        </p>

        <div class="social-link">
            <Image src={facebookIcon} alt="handy man sydney facebook" />
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/calldan2day">Facebook</a>
            <p>Give our facebook a visit! Donâ€™t forget to drop a like!</p>
